{
  "id": "adv_card_rei_53_02",
  "title": "一ノ瀬怜 2話 これも懐かしいわね",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokissa-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――三月八日　昼",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cafe-01.m4a",
          "delay": 1066.6667283,
          "startTime": 1.0666667283
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura Kawasaki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_53_02-skr001.m4a",
      "text": "あははっ、そんなことがあったんだ～。朝ご飯が\nマカロンだなんて、まさにお誕生日って感じだね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 6.0666667283,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokissa-00-noon",
      "startTime": 10.2666667283
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura Kawasaki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_53_02-skr002.m4a",
      "text": "それに、琴乃ちゃんと一緒に寝るなんて\n仲良しでいいな～。私も一緒にお泊まりしたかったよ～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 13.5000000616,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokissa-00-noon",
      "startTime": 19.2000000616
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei Ichinose",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_53_02-rei001.m4a",
      "text": "別にお泊まりはしてないけどね\nあと、さすがに三人でベッドに寝るのは狭いわよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 22.0666667283,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokissa-00-noon",
      "startTime": 26.1000010789
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura Kawasaki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_53_02-skr003.m4a",
      "text": "怜ちゃんのベッドだったら、大きいから大丈夫だよ～\n川咲さくらの、咲の字で寝よっか！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 30.3000000616,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokissa-00-noon",
      "startTime": 33.4000015875
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei Ichinose",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_53_02-rei002.m4a",
      "text": "普通にマットレスとか持って来なさいよ\nあと、多分それ川の字よね。組体操じゃないんだから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 36.4000000616,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokissa-00-noon",
      "startTime": 41.2666682542
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura Kawasaki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_53_02-skr004.m4a",
      "text": "おぉ～、怜ちゃん鋭い！　10ポイント！\nあ、遠慮しないで沢山頼んでね、今日は私の奢りだから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 45.3689409815,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_paper-01.m4a",
          "delay": 8664.392353899999,
          "startTime": 54.0333333354
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokissa-00-noon",
      "startTime": 45.3689409815
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokissa-00-noon",
      "startTime": 51.1666659654
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei Ichinose",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_53_02-rei003.m4a",
      "text": "えぇ、ありがとう、さくら。じゃあどれにしようかしら\nふふ、誕生日っていいことづくしね！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 56.4666666687,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokissa-00-noon",
      "startTime": 60.7333333354
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono Nagase",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_53_02-ktn001.m4a",
      "text": "――それで？　どうしてこんなことになってる訳？\nわざわざ昼休みに抜け出すはめになったんだからね？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 66.200000002,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokissa-00-noon",
      "startTime": 69.9000008245
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura Kawasaki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_53_02-skr005.m4a",
      "text": "いやぁ、それが……\nと、とにかく、ありがとう、琴乃ちゃん！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 74.8666666687,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokissa-00-noon",
      "startTime": 74.8666666687
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokissa-00-noon",
      "startTime": 78.7000008245
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei Ichinose",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_53_02-rei004.m4a",
      "text": "まさか二人ともお財布を忘れるなんて思わないじゃない\n現金払いのみだし……これはもう奇跡よね。あはは……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 83.400000002,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokissa-00-noon",
      "startTime": 91.666670543
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono Nagase",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_53_02-ktn002.m4a",
      "text": "ちょうど学校にいたからいいけど……。っていうか\nどっちかが実家に戻れば良かったんじゃないの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 96.1333333354,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokissa-00-noon",
      "startTime": 99.2000038763
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei Ichinose",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_53_02-rei005.m4a",
      "text": "た、確かにその手もあったわね。さすがにお母さん達に\nそんな姿を見せるのはあれだけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 104.0666666687,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokissa-00-noon",
      "startTime": 107.0000038763
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokissa-00-noon",
      "startTime": 109.6066666687
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono Nagase",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_53_02-ktn003.m4a",
      "text": "まったく……でも、せっかくだから\n私も食べていこうかしら。さくらの奢りみたいだし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 111.500000002,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokissa-00-noon",
      "startTime": 116.466670543
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura Kawasaki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_53_02-skr006.m4a",
      "text": "くぅ～！　もちろんっ！　命の恩人だし、好きなもの\n頼んじゃって！　一旦、お会計は任せちゃうけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 121.5333333354,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_coast-01.m4a",
          "delay": 6200.006926100003,
          "startTime": 127.7333402615
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_coast-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "3d_corridor_night",
      "startTime": 127.4833402615
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei Ichinose",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_53_02-rei006.m4a",
      "text": "それじゃあ、私達は東京でお仕事があるから\n琴乃も、授業中に居眠りしないように気をつけなさいね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 132.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono Nagase",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_53_02-ktn004.m4a",
      "text": "だ、大丈夫だってば。この後、体育だし\nお仕事の後の学校は、確かに眠たいけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 141.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura Kawasaki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_53_02-skr007.m4a",
      "text": "でも、それだけ充実してるってことだよ\nサニピも、月ストも、朝から大忙しなくらいに",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 148.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei Ichinose",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_53_02-rei007.m4a",
      "text": "そうね。朝といえば、昔よくここでランニング\nしていたわね。それが、今じゃ朝からお仕事だなんて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 157.7651055939,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono Nagase",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_53_02-ktn005.m4a",
      "text": "懐かしがってるところ悪いけど、のんびりしてると\n今日も走ることになっちゃうんじゃない？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 167.0666829426,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-out-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 8199.98372409998,
          "startTime": 175.2666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura Kawasaki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_53_02-skr008.m4a",
      "text": "わぁ！？　本当だよ、怜ちゃん！\nよーし、こうなったら、駅まで競走だー！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 172.400016276,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-out-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 12433.317057300002,
          "startTime": 184.8333333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei Ichinose",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_53_02-rei008.m4a",
      "text": "さくら！？　もう、なんで競走する必要があるのよ\nでも、これも懐かしいわね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 183.2666727701,
      "sfxList": []
    }
  ]
}